      "notes": "\n* ''Runic Blade's'' duration refreshes whenever ''Riven'' gains or consumes a stack.\n* The bonus damage applies {{sti|life steal}}.\n* ''Runic Blade'' does not affect structures (charges are not consumed when attacking them).\n* ''Runic Blade'' can be {{ai|Aegis Protection|Pantheon|blocked}}, {{ai|Counter Strike|Jax|dodged}}, or {{ai|Riposte|Fiora|parried}}.\n* ''Runic Blade'' charges are not be consumed if ''Riven'' is {{tip|blind|blinded}} when landing the enhanced attack.\n* ''Runic Blade'' charges do not proc against wards.",
